headline: Celebrating India's Retail Heroes with Coca-Cola's 'Locally Yours' Campaign
summary: The first to open, the last to close, and always at the center of community life. For decades, India's local retailers have stood at the helm of everyday life, knowing their customers by name, keeping festivals supplied, and turning shops into spaces of conversations, stories and tradition. With 'Locally Yours', Coca-Cola India celebrates these real-life heroes who make communities thrive.

headline: Coca-Cola® and Star Wars Unite to Celebrate Connection and the Uplifting Power of Fandom with New Campaign
summary: Coca-Cola® and Disney today announced a thrilling new collaboration to unite fans from across the galaxy, "Coca-Cola x Star Wars: Refresh Your Galaxy," celebrating the uplifting power of fandom and community. Building on Coca-Cola's 70-year relationship with Disney, this global campaign spotlights the power of Star Wars fandom that unites and drives us to create and celebrate meaningful human connections.
